item.title: About
item.description: Hello there. I am Kory Donati, a husband, father and data science nerd. I am writing this blog because I wanted to have a name for myself in the data science community. When I am not spending time with my family, I love to read Sci-Fi books, watch movies and play videogames. I have a job working on the data team for a local school district. I also work for a bootcamp where I mentor students studying to be their own data scientists.
